(80,	80,	'Olicek',	'form-selectize',	'Form extension for Nette framework which implement http://brianreavis.github.io/selectize.js/',	'MARKDOWN',	NULL,	5,	585,	5,	1,	4,	NULL,	NULL,	'form-selectize\n==============\n\nForm extension for Nette framework\n\n## Requirements\n\n* Nette 2.2+\n* jQuery 1.8+\n* [Selectize] (https://github.com/brianreavis/selectize.js)\n\n## Installation\n\nThe best way to install olicek/form-selectize is using  [Composer](http://getcomposer.org/):\n\n```sh\n$ composer require olicek/form-selectize:dev-master\n```\n\nAfter installation server site, you have to install client site. \nDownload from [brianreavis/selectize.js](https://github.com/brianreavis/selectize.js/tree/master/dist) or use [bower](http://bower.io/search/?q=selectize)\n\nNext step is copy [server-site](https://github.com/Olicek/form-selectize/blob/master/client-side/selectize.js) script from this extension to www dir and link it to appliacation.\n\nLast step is enable the extension using your neon config\n\n```\nextensions:\n	selectize: App\\Form\\Control\\SelectizeExtension\n```\n\n## Default configuration\n\n```\nselectize:\n	mode: full # second mode is `select` for selection just 1 option\n	create: on\n	maxItems: null\n	delimiter: #/\n	plugins:\n		- remove_button\n	valueField: id\n	labelField: name\n	searchField: name\n```\n\n\n## Data in array for full mode\n\n```\narray (2)\n	0 => array (2)\n		id => 1\n		name => \"First item\"\n	1 => array (2)\n		id => 2\n		name => \"Second item\"\n```\nid is set as valueField and name as labelField and searchField in config.neon. You can use whatever, have to just set in config.neon or in addSelectize method. For example: \n```\nvalueField: slug\n```\n\n## Using\n\n#### Default settings from config.neon\n\n```php\n$form->addSelectize(\'tags\', \'≈°t√≠tky\', $arrayData);\n```\n\n#### custome settings in method first way (array)\n```php\n$form->addSelectize(\'tags\', \'≈°t√≠tky\', $arrayData, [\'create\' => false, \'maxItems\' => 3]);\n```\n\n#### custome settings in method first way (method)\n\n```php\n$form->addSelectize(\'tags\', \'≈°t√≠tky\', $arrayData)->setValueField(\'slug\')->delimiter(\'_\');\n```\n\n## Output is:\n\n#### Select mode\n\n```\ndump($form->values->tags); // return \"1\"\n```\n\n#### Full mode\nIn full mode it will return array with valueField values. If you create some new tag, it will in sub array with plain text.\n\n```\narray (3)\n	0 => \"1\"\n	1 => \"2\"\n	new => array (1)\n		0 => \"Third item\"\n```\n',	'{\"github\":{\"composer\":{\"name\":\"composer.json\",\"path\":\"composer.json\",\"sha\":\"751cc272e40ab028fa21e7635006eeafb356b801\",\"size\":462,\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/api.github.com\\/repos\\/Olicek\\/form-selectize\\/contents\\/composer.json?ref=master\",\"html_url\":\"https:\\/\\/github.com\\/Olicek\\/form-selectize\\/blob\\/master\\/composer.json\",\"git_url\":\"https:\\/\\/api.github.com\\/repos\\/Olicek\\/form-selectize\\/git\\/blobs\\/751cc272e40ab028fa21e7635006eeafb356b801\",\"download_url\":\"https:\\/\\/raw.githubusercontent.com\\/Olicek\\/form-selectize\\/master\\/composer.json\",\"type\":\"file\",\"content\":\"ewoJIm5hbWUiOiAib2xpY2VrL2Zvcm0tc2VsZWN0aXplIiwKCSJkZXNjcmlw\\ndGlvbiI6ICJGb3JtIGV4dGVuc2lvbiBmb3IgTmV0dGUgZnJhbWV3b3JrIiwK\\nCSJob21lcGFnZSI6ICJodHRwczovL2dpdGh1Yi5jb20vT2xpY2VrL2Zvcm0t\\nc2VsZWN0aXplIiwKCSJsaWNlbnNlIjogIkdQTC0zLjAiLAoJImF1dGhvcnMi\\nOiBbCgkJewoJCQkibmFtZSI6ICJQZXRyIE9sacWhYXIiLAoJCQkiaG9tZXBh\\nZ2UiOiAiaHR0cDovL29saXNhci5ldSIKCQl9CgldLAoJInJlcXVpcmUiOiB7\\nCgkJInBocCI6ICI+PSA1LjQuMCIsCgkJIm5ldHRlL2RpIjogIj49IDIuMi4w\\nIiwKCQkibmV0dGUvZm9ybXMiOiAiPj0gMi4yLjAiLAoJCSJuZXR0ZS9waHAt\\nZ2VuZXJhdG9yIjogIj49IDIuMi4wIiwKCQkibmV0dGUvdXRpbHMiOiAiPj0g\\nMi4yLjAiCgkJCgl9LAoJImF1dG9sb2FkIjogewoJCSJjbGFzc21hcCI6IFsi\\nc3JjLyJdCgl9Cn0K\\n\",\"encoding\":\"base64\",\"_links\":{\"self\":\"https:\\/\\/api.github.com\\/repos\\/Olicek\\/form-selectize\\/contents\\/composer.json?ref=master\",\"git\":\"https:\\/\\/api.github.com\\/repos\\/Olicek\\/form-sel