(94,	94,	'AntikCz',	'jquery-nette-forms',	'Addition for NetteForms',	'MARKDOWN',	NULL,	1,	NULL,	1,	2,	0,	NULL,	NULL,	'# Client-side pro Nette forms\r\n\r\n## Instalace\r\n\r\n```html\r\n<script src=\"{$basePath}/js/jquery.js\"></script>\r\n<script src=\"{$basePath}/js/netteForms.js\"></script>\r\n<script src=\"{$basePath}/js/jquery.nette.forms.js\"></script>\r\n<script>\r\n    $.form.init();\r\n</script>\r\n```\r\n\r\n## Konfigurace\r\n\r\n```html\r\n    $.form.liveValidationUrl = {link validate!}; // Optional - Glob√°ln√≠ nastaven√≠ pro live validaci\r\n    $.form.useLabels = true; // V√Ωchoz√≠ true - P≈ôi hodnotƒõ true a p≈ôi renderu chyb u formul√°≈ôe bere label pole a p≈ôid√° k chybov√© zpr√°vƒõ\r\n```\r\n\r\nPro dynamicky p≈ôidan√© formul√°≈ôe m≈Ø≈æeme p≈ôi≈ôadit validaci za pomoc√≠:\r\n\r\n```html\r\n    $.form.refresh();\r\n```\r\n\r\n## Nastaven√≠ formul√°≈ôe p≈ôes data atributy\r\n\r\n### data-novalidate\r\n\r\nVynech√° validaci cel√©ho formul√°≈ôe.\r\n\r\n```html\r\n    <form n:name=\"name\" data-novalidate>\r\n```\r\n\r\n### data-novalidatelive\r\n\r\nVynech√° live validaci cel√©ho formul√°≈ôe.\r\n\r\n```html\r\n    <form n:name=\"name\" data-novalidatelive>\r\n```\r\n\r\n### data-error-container\r\n\r\nNastav√≠ vlastn√≠ container pro chybov√© hl√°≈°ky\r\n\r\n```html\r\n    <div id=\"myContainer\"></div>\r\n    \r\n    <form n:name=\"name\" data-error-container=\"#myContainer\">\r\n```\r\n\r\n### data-error-type\r\n\r\nNastav√≠ container pro jednu chybovou hl√°≈°ku.\r\n\r\n```html\r\n    <form n:name=\"name\" data-error-type=\"strong class=\'input-error\'\">\r\n```\r\n\r\nVygeneruje:\r\n\r\n```html\r\n    <div class=\"form-error-container\">\r\n        <strong class=\"input-error\">Tato polo≈æka je povinn√°.</strong>\r\n    </div>\r\n```\r\n\r\n### data-renderer \r\n\r\nNastav√≠ renderer.\r\n\r\n```html\r\n    <form n:name=\"name\" data-renderer=\"myRenderer\">\r\n```\r\n\r\n### data-nolabel\r\n\r\nVynech√° chybovou hl√°≈°ku s label.\r\n\r\n```html\r\n    <form n:name=\"name\" data-nolabel>\r\n```\r\n\r\n### data-errors-at\r\n\r\n```html\r\n    <form n:name=\"name\" data-errors-at=\"form\">\r\n```\r\n\r\nNastav√≠ vykreslovan√≠ chyb u formul√°≈ôe m√≠sto u input≈Ø.\r\n\r\n## Nastaven√≠ pole p≈ôes data atributy\r\n\r\n### data-validatelive-url\r\n\r\nNa danou url adresu se po≈°lou √∫daje k vyhodnocen√≠.\r\n\r\n```html\r\n    <input n:name=\"name\" data-validatelive-url=\"{link validateName!}\">\r\n```\r\n\r\n### data-novalidatelive\r\n\r\nLive validace se u tohoto pole neprovede\r\n\r\n```html\r\n    <input n:name=\"name\" data-novalidatelive>\r\n```\r\n\r\n### data-error-container\r\n\r\nNastav√≠ vlastn√≠ container pro chybov√© hl√°≈°ky\r\n\r\n```html\r\n    <input n:name=\"name\" data-error-container=\"#customContainer\">\r\n    \r\n    <div id=\"customContainer\"></div>\r\n```\r\n\r\n### data-error-type\r\n\r\nNastav√≠ container pro jednu chybovou hl√°≈°ku.\r\n\r\n```html\r\n    <input n:name=\"name\" data-error-type=\"strong class=\'input-error\'\">\r\n```\r\n\r\nVygeneruje:\r\n\r\n```html\r\n    <div class=\"form-error-container\">\r\n        <strong class=\"input-error\">Tato polo≈æka je povinn√°.</strong>\r\n    </div>\r\n```\r\n\r\n### data-novalidate\r\n\r\nPole bude p≈ôeskoƒçeno p≈ôi validaci.\r\n\r\n```html\r\n    <input n:name=\"name\" data-novalidate>\r\n```\r\n\r\n### data-label\r\n\r\nNastav√≠ label pro chybovou hl√°≈°ku.\r\n\r\n```html\r\n    <input n:name=\"name\" data-label=\"U≈æivatelsk√© jm√©no\">\r\n```\r\n\r\n### data-nolabel\r\n\r\nVynech√° chybovou hl√°≈°ku s label.\r\n\r\n```html\r\n    <input n:name=\"name\" data-nolabel>\r\n```\r\n\r\n## Nastaven√≠ odes√≠lac√≠ch tlaƒç√≠tek p≈ôes data atributy\r\n\r\n### data-novalidate\r\n\r\nVynech√° validaci formul√°≈ôe po kliknut√≠ na dan√© tlaƒç√≠tko.\r\n\r\n```html\r\n    <input n:name=\"back\" data-novalidate>\r\n```\r\n\r\n## Vlastn√≠ renderery\r\n\r\n```javascript\r\n\r\n$.form.addRenderer(\'render\', {\r\n    /**\r\n     * Error at control\r\n     *\r\n     * @param {string} message\r\n     * @param {SingleControl} ctrl\r\n     */\r\n    controlError: function (message, ctrl) {\r\n        // Odstranƒõn√≠ chyby u pole\r\n    },\r\n    /**\r\n     * Errors at form\r\n     *\r\n     * @param {string} message\r\n     * @param {SingleControl} ctrl\r\n     */\r\n    formError: function (message, ctrl) {\r\n        // P≈ôid√°n√≠ chyby u formul√°≈ôe\r\n    },\r\n    /**\r\n     * Base method for adding error message\r\n     *\r\n     * @param {string} message\r\n     * @param $container\r\n     * @param {SingleControl} ctrl\r\n     * @param {string} type\r\n     */\r\n    addError: function (message, $container, ctrl, type) {\r\n        // P≈ôid√°n√≠ chyby\r\n    },\r\n    /**\r\n     * Base method for removing error message\r\n     *\r\n     * @param $container\r\n     * @param {SingleControl} ctrl\r\n     */\r\n    removeCustomError: function ($container, ctrl) {\r\n        // Odstranƒõn√≠ chyby \r\n    },\r\n    /**\r\n     * Method which removes error message at control\r\n     *\r\n     * @param {SingleControl} ctrl\r\n     */\r\n    removeError: function (ctrl) {\r\n        // Odstranƒõn√≠ chyby u pole\r\n    },\r\n    /**\r\n     * Method which removes error message at form\r\n     *\r\n     * @param {SingleControl} ctrl\r\n     */\r\n    removeFormError: function (ctrl) {\r\n        // Odstranƒõn√≠ chyby u formul√°≈ôe\r\n    }\r\n});\r\n\r\n```',	'{\"github\":{\"readme\":{\"name\":\"README.md\",\"path\":\"README.md\",\"sha\":\"2ba4c4a8bca7c709d83f92143fd659a61a283d9d\",\"size\":4768,\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/api.github.com\\/repos\\/AntikCz\\/jquery-nette-forms\\/contents\\/README.md?ref=master\",\"html_url\":\"https:\\/\\/github.com\\/AntikCz\\/jquery-nette-forms\\/blob\\/master\\/README.md\",\"git_url\":\"https:\\/\\/api.github.com\\/repos\\/AntikCz\\/jquery-nette-forms\\/git\\/blobs\\/2ba4c4a8bca7c709d83f92143fd659a61a283d9d\",\"download_url\":\"https:\\/\\/raw.githubusercontent.com\\/AntikCz\\/jquery-nette-form