(110,	110,	'nedryse',	'translateable-template-factory',	'Proper way how to load translator into the presenters and controls template in the Nette framework based applications',	'MARKDOWN',	NULL,	1,	27,	1,	0,	0,	NULL,	'nette,translator,dry,nedryse',	'#nedryse/translateable-template-factory (cc)#\nPavel ≈Ωelezn√Ω (2bfree), 2014 ([pavelzelezny.cz](http://pavelzelezny.cz))\n\n## Requirements ##\n\n[Nette Framework 2.2.0](http://nette.org) or higher\n\n## Documentation ##\n\nProper way how to load translator into the presenters and controls template in the Nette framework based applications\n\n## Instalation ##\n\nPrefered way to intall is by the [Composer](http://getcomposer.org)\n\n	composer require nedryse/translateable-template-factory:~1.0.0\n\nOr by manualy adding into the [composer.json](https://getcomposer.org/doc/04-schema.md#json-schema)\n\n	{\n		\"require\":{\n			\"nedryse/translateable-template-factory\": \"~1.0.0\"\n		}\n	}\n\n## Setup ##\n\nAdd following code into the [config.neon](http://doc.nette.org/en/2.2/configuring#toc-framework-configuration)\n\n	common:\n		services:\n			nette.templateFactory: Nedryse\\Nette\\Bridges\\ApplicationLatte\\TranslatableTemplateFactory\n\n## Usage ##\nAt the moment of the template creation in the presenter or in the control, the translator is already loaded in it',	'{\"github\":{\"composer\":{\"name\":\"composer.json\",\"path\":\"composer.json\",\"sha\":\"509170bd98724bfe951ae5952eb1e02c4751d488\",\"size\":775,\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/api.github.com\\/repos\\/nedryse\\/translateable-template-factory\\/contents\\/composer.json?ref=master\",\"html_url\":\"https:\\/\\/github.com\\/nedryse\\/translateable-template-factory\\/blob\\/master\\/composer.json\",\"git_url\":\"https:\\/\\/api.github.com\\/repos\\/nedryse\\/translateable-template-factory\\/git\\/blobs\\/509170bd98724bfe951ae5952eb1e02c4751d488\",\"download_url\":\"https:\\/\\/raw.githubusercontent.com\\/nedryse\\/translateable-template-factory\\/master\\/composer.json\",\