(148,	148,	'Majkl578',	'nette-identity-doctrine',	'Integration of Doctrine entities implementing IIdentity in Nette 2.1+',	'MARKDOWN',	NULL,	18,	5302,	18,	3,	9,	NULL,	'nette,doctrine,orm,security,identity,authentication',	'# Nette 2 & Doctrine 2 entities\n\nNette addon for using Doctrine 2 entities directly as Nette identity\n\n\n## Motivation\n\nIf you are using Nette 2 and Doctrine 2 together, you will sooner or later\nwant to use some of your entities also as identity, because it is practical.\n\nFortunately, this addon is here to help you with this task!\n\n\n## Requirements\n\n- PHP 5.3.2+\n- Nette 2.2+\n- Doctrine ORM 2.3+\n\n\n## Installation\n\n1. Install via composer:\n\n   `composer require majkl578/nette-identity-doctrine`\n\n2. Register extension in your configuration file in extensions section:\n    ```yaml\n    extensions:\n        doctrine2identity: Majkl578\\NetteAddons\\Doctrine2Identity\\DI\\IdentityExtension\n    ```\n\n3. Delete cache.\n\nYou\'re done. ;)\n\n\n## Usage\n\nImagine you have an application where you\'re implementing authentication.\nAll you have is a regular entity for the user in your application.\nNow you want to implement the authentication itself - you need to have an identity.\nThe only thing you have to do is to implement `Nette\\Security\\IIdentity` on your user entity,\nso you get something like this:\n\n```php\nuse Doctrine\\ORM\\Mapping as ORM;\n\n/**\n * @ORM\\Entity\n */\nclass UserEntity implements IIdentity\n{\n	/** @ORM\\Column(type=\"integer\") @ORM\\Id @ORM\\GeneratedValue */\n	private $id;\n\n	/** @ORM\\Column */\n	private $name;\n\n	... other properties, getters & setters\n\n	/* implementation of IIdentity */\n	public function getId()\n	{\n		return $this->id;\n	}\n\n	public function getRoles()\n	{\n		return array();\n	}\n}\n```\n\n(Notice the empty getRoles() method. That is due to the requirement of IIdentity.\nIf you don\'t use authorization, unfortunately, it can\'t be omitted, sorry.)\n\nThat\'s all. Everything is automatic!\nAnd you can even use entities with composite identifiers!\n\n\n## Issues\n\nIn case of any problems, just leave an issue here on GitHub (or, better, send a pull request).\n',	'{\"github\":{\"composer\":{\"name\":\"composer.json\",\"path\":\"composer.json\",\"sha\":\"274e7c2807fa997273d98265e9ebe4db34e4f61b\",\"size\":852,\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/api.github.com\\/repos\\/Majkl578\\/nette-identity-doctrine\\/contents\\/composer.json?ref=master\",\"html_url\":\"https:\\/\\/github.com\\/Majkl578\\/nette-identity-doctrine\\/blob\\/master\\/composer.json\",\"git_url\":\"https:\\/\\/api.github.com\\/repos\\/Majkl578\\/nette-identity-doctrine\\/git\\/blobs\\/274e7c2807fa997273d98265e9ebe4db34e4f61b\",\"download_url\":\"https:\\/\\/raw.githubusercontent.com\\/Majkl578\\/nette-identity-doctrine\\/master\\/composer.json\",\"type\":\"file\",\"content\":\"ewoJIm5hbWUiOiAibWFqa2w1NzgvbmV0dGUtaWRlbnRpdHktZG9jdHJpbmUi\\nLAoJInR5cGUiOiAibmV0dGUtYWRkb24iLAoJImtleXdvcmRzIjogWyJuZXR0\\nZSIsICJkb2N0cmluZSIsICJvcm0iLCAic2VjdXJpdHkiLCAiaWRlbnRpdHki\\nLCAiYXV0aGVudGljYXRpb24iXSwKCSJhdXRob3JzIjogWwoJCXsKCQkJIm5h\\nbWUiOiAiTWljaGFlbCBNb3JhdmVjIgoJCX0KCV0sCgkiZGVzY3JpcHRpb24i\\nOiAiSW50ZWdyYXRpb24gb2YgZW50aXRpZXMgaW1wbGVtZW50aW5nIElJZGVu\\ndGl0eSBpbiBOZXR0ZSAyIiwKCSJsaWNlbnNlIjogIk1JVCIsCgkicmVxdWly\\nZSI6IHsKCQkicGhwIjogIj49NS4zLjIiLAoJCSJuZXR0ZS9kaSI6ICJ+Mi4y\\nIiwKCQkibmV0dGUvaHR0cCI6ICJ+Mi4yIiwKCQkibmV0dGUvc2VjdXJpdHki\\nOiAifjIuMiIsCgkJImRvY3RyaW5lL29ybSI6ICJ+Mi4zIgoJfSwKCSJyZXF1\\naXJlLWRldiI6IHsKCQkibmV0dGUvYm9vdHN0cmFwIjogIn4yLjIiLAoJCSJr\\nZHlieS9kb2N0cmluZSI6ICJ+Mi4wIiwKCQkidHJhY3kvdHJhY3kiOiAifjIu\\nMiIsCgkJInBocHVuaXQvcGhwdW5pdCI6ICJ+NC44IgoJfSwKCSJzdWdnZXN0\\ncyI6IHsKCQkibmV0dGUvYm9vdHN0cmFwIjogIlRvIHVzZSBJZGVudGl0eUV4\\ndGVuc2lvbjo6cmVnaXN0ZXIoKS4iCgl9LAoJImF1dG9sb2FkIjogewoJCSJw\\nc3ItNCI6IHsKCQkJIk1hamtsNTc4XFxOZXR0ZUFkZG9uc1xcRG9jdHJpbmUy\\nSWRlbnRpdHlcXCI6ICJsaWIiCgkJfQoJfSwKCSJhdXRvbG9hZC1kZXYiOiB7\\nCgkJInBzci00IjogewoJCQkiTWFqa2w1NzhcXE5ldHRlQWRkb25zXFxEb2N0