æit√≠ jako app_name. Tyto dvƒõ polo≈æky aktu√°lnƒõ nejsou povinn√©, nicm√©nƒõ s postupn√Ωm roz≈°√≠≈ôov√°n√≠m knihovny o generov√°n√≠ Request≈Ø a Wallpost≈Ø se budou hodit.</td>\n	</tr>\n	<tr>\n		<th>scope</th>\n		<td>string, string, string....; nepovinn√©</td>\n		<td>Extended permissions pro aplikaci, viz http://developers.facebook.com/docs/authentication/permissions/#extended_perms</td>\n	</tr>\n</table>\n\n## 4. Pou≈æit√≠\n\nK√≥d naleznete v `examples/presenter-usage`.\n\n#### `HomepagePresenter.php`\n```php\n<?php\n\nuse Nette\\Diagnostics\\Debugger;\n\nclass HomepagePresenter extends BasePresenter\n{\n\n    public function renderDefault()\n    {\n        // Autorizoval u≈æivatel na≈°i aplikaci?\n        if ($this->facebookConnect->isLoggedIn() === FALSE)\n        {\n            // Volitelnƒõ m≈Ø≈æeme zmƒõnit URL, na kterou bude u≈æivatel z Facebooku navr√°cen\n            // P≈ôij√≠m√° buƒè nette z√°pis odkaz≈Ø nebo absolutn√≠ URL\n            $this->facebookConnect->setRedirectUri(\"Homepage:default\");\n\n\n            // P≈ôihl√°s√≠me ho p≈ôesmƒõrov√°n√≠m na Login_URL\n            $this->facebookConnect->login();\n        }\n        else // U≈æivatel je p≈ôihl√°≈°en√Ω v aplikaci\n        {\n            /* @var $user Illagrenan\\Facebook\\FacebookUser */\n            $user                 = $this->facebookConnect->getFacebookUser();\n            $this->template->user = $user;\n\n            Debugger::dump($user);\n        }\n    }\n\n    /**\n     * P≈ôesmƒõruje u≈æivatele na p≈ôihla≈°ovac√≠ str√°nku aplikace (na facebook.com)\n     */\n    public function handleFacebookLogin()\n    {\n        $this->facebookConnect->login();\n    }\n\n    /**\n     * Odhl√°s√≠ u≈æivatele z aplikace A z Facebooku\n     */\n    public function handleFacebookLogout()\n    {\n        $this->facebookConnect->logout();\n    }\n\n}\n?>\n```\n\n#### `default.latte`\n\nK√≥d naleznete v `examples/latte-usage`.\n\n```html\n{block #content}\n    <h1>Nette FacebookConnect</h1>\n\n    {ifs