(180,	180,	'romanmatyus',	'FileMailer',	'Addon for catch mails in Nette to filesystem and showing it in debug bar.',	'MARKDOWN',	NULL,	7,	370,	7,	1,	3,	NULL,	'nette,mailer,mail,debugbar,debuging',	'# FileMailer\nE-mails catching addon for [Nette Framework](http://nette.org). Emails are stored into files and shown in Tracy bar.\n\n**!WARNING!** - After setting up this addon, all e-mails are not sent, but ONLY stored on filesystem and shown in Tracy bar.\n\n![Demo](http://i41.tinypic.com/t9uuzq.png)\n\n\n## Killer features\n- Simple instalation\n- Extensive configuration options\n- Full access to headers\n- Plain text and HTML output\n- Possibility to download the attachments\n- Parser caching\n\n\n## Installation\nAdd package to your project by the [Composer](https://getcomposer.org/):\n```\ncomposer require rm/filemailer\n```\n\nor download addon manually from [GitHub](https://github.com/romanmatyus/FileMailer/releases) and unpack it in place indexed by RobotLoader.\n\n\n## Configuration\nThe addon consists of two parts. The first one is the `FileMailer` which replaces the [IMailer](api.nette.org/Nette.Mail.IMailer.html) service and stores e-mails to filesystem. The second one is the `MailPanel` which is the Tracy bar panel and shows e-mails stored by FileMailer.\n\nDefault options are used in following examples.\n\n### Setup by extension\nRegister new compiler extension in `config.neon` and optionally configure:\n```\nextensions:\n	mailer: RM\\MailPanel\\DI\\MailPanelExtension\n\nmailer:\n	newMessageTime: \'-2 seconds\'    # how long consider email as new\n	show: [subject, from, to]       # which headers show in overview\n	autoremove: \'-5 seconds\'        # how old emails are purged\n	hideEmpty: yes                  # hide bar icon when no emails?\n	debugger: yes                   # enable Tracy bar\n	tempDir: \'%tempDir/mails\'       # change e-mails store directory\n```\n\n### Manual setup\nReplace the Nette\'s default IMailer service and register Tracy bar panel:\n```\nservices:\n	mail.mailer: RM\\FileMailer(%tempDir%/mails)\n\n	mailerPanel:\n		class: RM\\MailPanel\n		autowired: no\n		setup:\n			- setFileMailer(@mail.mailer)	# required\n			- $newMessageTime(\'-5 seconds\')\n			- $show([subject, from, to])\n			- $autoremove(\'-5 seconds\')\n			- $hideEmpty(yes)\n\ntracy:\n	bar:\n		- @mailerPanel\n```\n',	'{\"github\":{\"composer\":{\"name\":\"composer.json\",\"path\":\"composer.json\",\"sha\":\"75f078047b8c2d41ea4a58f1a5ddb16ddde4f6ce\",\"size\":652,\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/api.github.com\\/repos\\/romanmatyus\\/FileMailer\\/contents\\/composer.json?ref=master\",\"html_url\":\"https:\\/\\/github.com\\/romanmatyus\\/FileMailer\\/blob\\/master\\/composer.json\",\"git_url\":\"https:\\/\\/api.github.com\\/repos\\/romanmatyus\\/FileMailer\\/git\\/blobs\\/75f078047b8c2d41ea4a58f1a5ddb16ddde4f6ce\",\"download_url\":\"https:\\/\\/raw.githubusercontent.com\\/romanmatyus\\/FileMailer\\/master\\/composer.json\",\"type\":\"file\",\"content\":\"ewoJIm5hbWUiOiAicm0vZmlsZW1haWxlciIsCgkidHlwZSI6ICJsaWJyYXJ5\\nIiwKCSJ2ZXJzaW9uIjogIjAuMy4yIiwKCSJkZXNjcmlwdGlvbiI6ICJBZGRv\\nbiBmb3IgY2F0Y2hpbmcgZS1tYWlscyBpbiBOZXR0ZSBGVyB0byBmaWxlc3lz\\ndGVtIGFuZCBzaG93aW5nIGl0IGluIHRoZSBEZWJ1ZyBCYXIuIiwKCSJrZXl3\\nb3JkcyI6IFsibmV0dGUiLCAibWFpbGVyIiwgIm1haWwiLCAiZGVidWdiYXIi\\nLCAiZGVidWdpbmciXSwKCSJob21lcGFnZSI6ICJodHRwczovL2dpdGh1Yi5j\\nb20vcm9tYW5tYXR5dXMvRmlsZU1haWxlciIsCgkibGljZW5zZSI6IFsiTUlU\\nIl0sCgkiYXV0aG9ycyI6IFsKCQl7CgkJCSJuYW1lIjogIkphbiBEcsOhYmVr\\nIiwKCQkJIm5hbWUiOiAiUm9tYW4gTcOhdHl1cyIKCQl9CgldLAoJInJlcXVp\\ncmUiOiB7CgkJInBocCIgOiAiPj01LjQuMCIsCgkJIm5ldHRlL2FwcGxpY2F0\\naW9uIjogIj49Mi4yIiwKCQkibmV0dGUvY2FjaGluZyI6ICI+PTIuMiIsCgkJ\\nIm5ldHRlL2h0dHAiOiAiPj0yLjIiLAoJCSJuZXR0ZS9tYWlsIjogIj49Mi4y\\nIiwKCQkibmV0dGUvdXRpbHMiOiAiPj0yLjIiLAoJCSJsYXR0ZS9sYXR0ZSI6\\nICI+PTIuMiIKCX0sCgkiYXV0b2xvYWQiOiB7CgkJImNsYXNzbWFwIjogWyJz\\ncmMvRmlsZU1haWxlci8iXQoJfQp9Cg==\\n\",\"encoding\":\"base64\",\"_links\":{\"self\":\"https:\\/\\/api.github.com\\/repos\\/romanmaty