(201,	201,	'lookyman',	'mandrill',	'Send emails via Mandrill in Nette Framework',	'MARKDOWN',	NULL,	1,	12,	1,	0,	0,	NULL,	'Nette,Mandrill,mail',	'lookyman/Mandrill\n======\n\nSend emails via [Mandrill](https://mandrill.com) in Nette Framework.\n\n[![Build Status](https://travis-ci.org/lookyman/mandrill.svg?branch=master)](https://travis-ci.org/lookyman/mandrill)\n[![Downloads](https://img.shields.io/packagist/dt/lookyman/mandrill.svg)](https://packagist.org/packages/lookyman/mandrill)\n[![Latest stable](https://img.shields.io/packagist/v/lookyman/mandrill.svg)](https://packagist.org/packages/lookyman/mandrill)\n[![Code Climate](https://codeclimate.com/github/lookyman/mandrill/badges/gpa.svg)](https://codeclimate.com/github/lookyman/mandrill)\n\n\nRequirements\n------\n\nlookyman/Mandrill requires PHP 5.5 or higher.\n\n- [Nette Framework](https://github.com/nette/nette)\n\n\nInstallation\n------\n\nThe best way to install lookyman/Mandrill is using [Composer](http://getcomposer.org/):\n\n```sh\n$ composer require lookyman/mandrill\n```\n\nYou can enable the extension using your neon config:\n\n```yml\nextensions:\n	mandrill: lookyman\\Mandrill\\DI\\MandrillExtension\n```\n\n\nConfiguration\n------\n\nThis extension creates new configuration section `mandrill`, the default configuration looks like this:\n\n```yml\nmandrill:\n	apiKey: \'\'\n	format: \'json\'\n	endpointUrl: \'https://mandrillapp.com/api/1.0\'\n	debugger: off\n	client: []\n```\n\nYou can get your `apiKey` at the [Mandrill](https://mandrillapp.com) settings page.\n\nThe `client` configuration option can pass additional settings to the default [Guzzle](http://guzzlephp.org) client. For example, should you run into the `cURL error 60: SSL certificate problem: unable to get local issuer certificate` error, you can use the `verify: off` option here to disable peer certificate verification.\n\n\nUsage\n------\n\nThis extension provides you with the service `lookyman\\Mandrill\\Mandrill`, that you can inject into your application and use it to send a message.\n\n```php\n// $this->mandrill in an instance of lookyman\\Mandrill\\Mandrill\n\n$message = (new lookyman\\Mandrill\\Message\\Message)\n	->setFromEmail(\'sender@example.org\')\n	->addTo(\'recipient@example.org\');\n	->setText(\'Hello!\');\n\n$this->mandrill->send($message);\n```\n\n\n-----\n\nHomepage [https://lookyman.net](https://lookyman.net) and repository [https://github.com/lookyman/mandrill](https://github.com/lookyman/mandrill).\n',	'{\"github\":{\"composer\":{\"name\":\"composer.json\",\"path\":\"composer.json\",\"sha\":\"84ded04e8c1cf2a8c2e82a527ad7a389a3d82fde\",\"size\":682,\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/api.github.com\\/repos\\/lookyman\\/mandrill\\/contents\\/composer.json?ref=master\",\"html_url\":\"https:\\/\\/github.com\\/lookyman\\/mandrill\\/blob\\/master\\/composer.json\",\"git_url\":\"https:\\/\\/api.github.com\\/repos\\/lookyman\\/mandrill\\/git\\/blobs\\/84ded04e8c1cf2a8c2e82a527ad7a389a3d82fde\",\"download_url\":\"https:\\/\\/raw.githubusercontent.com\\/lookyman\\/mandrill\\/master\\/composer.json\",\"type\":\"file\",\"content\":\"ewoJIm5hbWUiOiAibG9va3ltYW4vbWFuZHJpbGwiLAoJImRlc2NyaXB0aW9u\\nIjogIiIsCgkia2V5d29yZHMiOiBbIk5ldHRlIiwgIk1hbmRyaWxsIiwgIm1h\\naWwiXSwKCSJsaWNlbnNlIjogWyJNSVQiXSwKCSJhdXRob3JzIjogWwoJCXsK\\nCQkJIm5hbWUiOiAiTHVrw6HFoSBVbmdlciIsCgkJCSJlbWFpbCI6ICJsb29r\\neS5tc2NAZ21haWwuY29tIiwKCQkJImhvbWVwYWdlIjogImh0dHBzOi8vbG9v\\na3ltYW4ubmV0IgoJCX0KCV0sCgkicmVxdWlyZSI6IHsKCQkicGhwIjogIj49\\nNS41IiwKCQkiZ3V6emxlaHR0cC9ndXp6bGUiOiAifjYuMCIsCgkJIm5ldHRl\\nL2RpIjogIn4yLjMiCgl9LAoJInJlcXVpcmUtZGV2IjogewoJCSJuZXR0ZS9y\\nb2JvdC1sb2FkZXIiOiAifjIuMyIsCgkJInBocHVuaXQvcGhwdW5pdCI6ICJ+\\nNC44IiwKCQkic3ltZm9ueS95YW1sIjogIn4yLjciLAoJCSJ0cmFjeS90cmFj\\neSI6ICJ+Mi4zIgoJfSwKCSJzdWdnZXN0IjogewoJCSJzeW1mb255L3lhbWwi\\nOiAiQWxsb3cgdXNpbmcgWUFNTCByZXNwb25zZSBmb3JtYXQuIiwKCQkidHJh\\nY3kvdHJhY3kiOiAiQWxsb3cgdHVybmluZyBvbiB0aGUgJ2RlYnVnZ2VyJyBj\\nb25maWd1cmF0aW9uIG9wdGlvbi4iCgl9LAoJImF1dG9sb2FkIjogewoJCSJw\\nc3ItNCI