(204,	204,	'Venne',	'widgets',	'',	'MARKDOWN',	NULL,	0,	159,	0,	0,	0,	NULL,	'nette,venne,widgets',	'# Venne:Widgets [![Build Status](https://secure.travis-ci.org/Venne/widgets.png)](http://travis-ci.org/Venne/widgets)\n\n\n## Installation\n\nThe best way to install Venne/Widgets is using Composer:\n\n```sh\ncomposer require venne/widgets:@dev\n```\n\n\n## Automatic usage\n\n### Register widgets\n\nUse tag `venne.widget`:\n\n```yaml\nservices:\n	myControlFactory:\n		class: App\\MyControlFactory\n		tags: [venne.widget: \'myWidget\']\n```\n\n### Use widgets in presenters/controls as global component\n\n```php\nclass ExamplePresenter extends Nette\\Application\\UI\\Presenter\n{\n	use Venne\\Widgets\\WidgetsControlTrait;\n}\n```\n\nTemplate:\n\n```smarty\n...\n{control myWidget}\n...\n```\n\n\n## Manual usage\n\n**Register some widgets**\n\n```php\n$widgetManager = new Venne\\Widgets\\WidgetManager($systemContainer);\n$widgetManager->addWidget(\'widget1\', function() {\n	return new MyComponent;\n});\n$widgetManager->addWidget(\'widget2\', new MyFormFactory);\n$widgetManager->addWidget(\'widget3\', \'app.myFormFactory\'); // service in system container\n```\n\n**Create instance and use it**\n\n```php\nif ($widgetManager->hasWidget(\'widget1\')) {\n	$widget = $widgetManager->getWidget(\'widget1\');\n	$widget->render();\n}\n```\n',	'{\"github\":{\"composer\":{\"name\":\"composer.json\",\"path\":\"composer.json\",\"sha\":\"caae5431605bac62c4af9b960b74c0f1827e5532\",\"size\":919,\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/api.github.com\\/repos\\/Venne\\/widgets\\/contents\\/composer.json?ref=master\",\"html_url\":\"https:\\/\\/github.com\\/Venne\\/widgets\\/blob\\/master\\/composer.json\",\"git_url\":\"https:\\/\\/api.github.com\\/repos\\/Venne\\/widgets\\/git\\/blobs\\/caae5431605bac62c4af9b960b74c0f1827e5532\",\"download_url\":\"https:\\/\\/raw.githubusercontent.com\\/Venne\\/widgets\\/master\\/composer.json\",\"type\":\"file\",\"content\":\"ewoJIm5hbWUiOiAidmVubmUvd2lkZ2V0cyIsCgkiZGVzY3JpcHRpb