(217,	217,	'VaclavSir',	'NBrowserKit',	'Implementation of Symfony\'s BrowserKit for Nette applications.',	'MARKDOWN',	NULL,	0,	2,	0,	0,	0,	NULL,	NULL,	'# NBrowserKit\n\nThis package implements [Symfony\'s BrowserKit](https://github.com/symfony/BrowserKit) Client for use with a [Nette](http://nette.org/) application.\n\n## Usage\n\n```php\n\n	$client = new Client;\n	$client->setContainer($container);\n\n	$client->request(\'GET\', \'/\');\n\n	Assert::same(200, $client->getResponse()->getStatus());\n	Assert::contains(\'Hello World\', $client->getResponse()->getContent());\n\n```\n\nYou can find more [examples in The Symfony Book](http://symfony.com/doc/current/book/testing.html#functional-tests).\n\nExample of usage with Nette and Nette Tester: https://github.com/VaclavSir/NBrowserKit-example\n\n## Running Tests\n\nTests for this package are written using [Nette Tester](http://tester.nette.org/) library. You can run them easily from the command line:\n\n```bash\n\n	composer install --dev\n	vendor/bin/tester tests\n\n```\n',	'{\"github\":{\"composer\":{\"name\":\"composer.json\",\"path\":\"composer.json\",\"sha\":\"d949e705458eef71c59cf865697da388b6c881b9\",\"size\":771,\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/api.github.com\\/repos\\/VaclavSir\\/NBrowserKit\\/contents\\/composer.json?ref=master\",\"html_url\":\"https:\\/\\/github.com\\/VaclavSir\\/NBrowserKit\\/blob\\/master\\/composer.json\",\"git_url\":\"https:\\/\\/api.github.com\\/repos\\/VaclavSir\\/NBrowserKit\\/git\\/blobs\\/d949e705458eef71c59cf865697da388b6c881b9\",\"download_url\":\"https:\\/\\/raw.githubusercontent.com\\/VaclavSir\\/NBrowserKit\\/master\\/composer.json\",\"type\":\"file\",\"content\":\"ewoJIm5hbWUiOiAidmFjbGF2LXNpci9uLWJyb3dzZXIta2l0IiwKCSJkZXNj\\ncmlwdGlvbiI6ICJJbXBsZW1lbnRhdGlvbiBvZiBTeW1mb255J3MgQnJvd3Nl\\ncktpdCBmb3IgTmV0dGUgYXBwbGljYXRpb25zLiIsCgkiaG9tZXBhZ2UiOiAi\\naHR0cDovL2dpdGh1Yi5jb20vVmFjbGF2U2lyL05Ccm93c2VyS2l0IiwKCSJ0\\neXBlIjogImxpYnJhcnkiLAoJImxpY2Vuc2UiOiBbIk1JVCJdLAoJImF1dGhv\\ncnMiOiBbCgkJewo