(222,	222,	'meridius',	'yadup',	'Database updator for Nette/Tracy panel',	'MARKDOWN',	NULL,	0,	17,	0,	1,	0,	NULL,	'yadup,database,db,updator,panel,nette,tracy',	'# Yadup - *Yet Another Database Updator Panel*\n*Database updator for [Nette/Tracy](https://github.com/nette/tracy) panel*\n\n\n## How to\n**For Nette 2.2 support please see the bottom.**\n\n1. Use the following [Composer](https://packagist.org/) command in your existing project to add Yadup to it:  \n\n        composer require meridius/yadup\n\n2. Register the extension by adding the following to your `config.neon` (1<sup>st</sup> level):  \n\n        extensions:\n        	yadup: Yadup\\YadupExtension\n\n3. And at last don\'t forget to create directory for SQL updates files. Default is `%appDir%/sql` as specified below.\n\n\n## Further configuration\nYou can tailor the updator to your needs by creating a new section `yadup` in `config.neon` (on the same level as `extensions`). Accepted parameters with their default values are following:\n\n```neon\nyadup:\n	dbUpdateTable: \'_db_update\'\n	dbConnection: \'@database.default\'\n	definerUser: \'\' # definer can be changed only in queries that already have one defined\n	definerHost: \'\'\n	sqlDir: \'%appDir%/sql\' # directory with sql script files\n	sqlExt: \'.sql\' # extension of sql files; with \'dot\'\n```\n	\n\n## Notes\nFor updator to work it is setting its own mapping to `Yadup\\\\*Module\\\\*Presenter` which shouldn\'t affect you in any way.\n\n**Full DB update** in used terminology is the one that should contain `DROP DATABASE` or at least `DROP TABLE` to prevent possible incompatibilities with consequent updates.\n\nFile naming format for SQL update files is `Y-m-d_H-i-s[_full].sql`\n\n\n\n## Nette 2.2 support\nBecause of incompatible changes in Nette/Database 2.3 the support for 2.2 version is moved to the separate Yadup 1.0 version which will receive support for at least some time.\n\n\n### Installation\n        composer require \"meridius/yadup ~1.0.0\"\n\n\n### Further configuration\nSame as above, instead of:\n```neon\nyadup:\n	dbConnection: \'@nette.database.default\'\n```\n\n',	'{\"github\":{\"composer\":{\"name\":\"composer.json\",\"path\":\"composer.json\",\"sha\":\"a5577529489a676b2c09c957032f33dfa7ef41da\",\"size\":652,\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/api.github.com\\/repos\\/meridius\\/yadup\\/contents\\/composer.json?ref=master\",\"html_url\":\"https:\\/\\/github.com\\/meridius\\/yadup\\/blob\\/master\\/composer.json\",\"git_url\":\"https:\\/\\/api.github.com\\/repos\\/meridius\\/yadup\\/git\\/blobs\\/a5577529489a676b2c09c957032f33dfa7ef41da\",\"download_url\":\"https:\\/\\/raw.githubusercontent.com\\/meridius\\/yadup\\/master\\/composer.json\",\"type\":\"file\",\"content\":\"ewoJIm5hbWUiOiAibWVyaWRpdXMveWFkdXAiLAoJInR5cGUiOiAibGlicmFy\\neSIsCgkiZGVzY3JpcHRpb24iOiAiRGF0YWJhc2UgdXBkYXRvciBmb3IgTmV0\\ndGUvVHJhY3kgcGFuZWwiLAoJImtleXdvcmRzIjogWyJ5YWR1cCIsICJkYXRh\\nYmFzZSIsICJkYiIsICJ1cGRhdG9yIiwgInBhbmVsIiwgIm5ldHRlIiwgInRy\\nYWN5Il0sCgkiaG9tZXBhZ2UiOiAiaHR0cHM6Ly9naXRodWIuY29tL21lcmlk\\naXVzL3lhZHVwIiwKCSJsaWNlbnNlIjogIkFwYWNoZS0yLjAiLAoJImF1dGhv\\ncnMiOiBbCgkJewoJCQkibmFtZSI6ICJNYXJ0aW4gTHVrZcWhIiwKCQkJImhv\\nbWVwYWdlIjogImh0dHBzOi8vZ2l0aHViLmNvbS9tZXJpZGl1cy95YWR1cCIK\\nCQl9CgldLAoJInN1cHBvcnQiOiB7CgkJImlzc3VlcyI6ICJodHRwczovL2dp\\ndGh1Yi5jb20vbWVyaWRpdXMveWFkdXAvaXNzdWVzIgoJfSwKCSJyZXF1aXJl\\nIjogewoJCSJuZXR0ZS9kaSI6ICJ+Mi4zLjAiLAoJCSJuZXR0ZS91dGlscyI6\\nICJ+Mi4zLjAiLAoJCSJuZXR0ZS9maW5kZXIiOiAifjIuMy4wIiwKCQkidHJh\\nY3kvdHJhY3kiOiAifjIuMy4wIiwKCQkibmV0dGUvZGF0YWJhc2UiOiAifjIu\\nMy4wIgoJfSwKCSJhdXRvbG9hZCI6IHsKCQkicHNyLTQiOiB7CgkJCSJZYWR1\\ncFxcIjogInNyYy8iCgkJfQoJfQp9Cg==\\n\",\"encoding\":\"base64\",\"_links\":{\"self\":\"https:\\/\\/api.github.com\\/repos\\/meridius\\/yadup\\/contents\\/composer.json?ref=master\",\"git\":\"https:\\/\\/api.github.com\\/repos\\/meridius\\/yadup\\/git\\/blobs\\/a5577529489a676b2c09c957032f33dfa7ef41da\",\"html\":\"https:\\/\\/github.com\\/meridius\\/yadup\\/blob\\/master\\/comp