(234,	234,	'zeleznypa',	'nette-session-debug-bar',	'Extension for Nette2 DebugPanel ',	'MARKDOWN',	NULL,	6,	198,	6,	4,	8,	NULL,	'nette,session,debug bar,tracy',	'#Session-DebugBar ([WTFPL](http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/WTFPL))#\nPavel ≈Ωelezn√Ω (2bfree), 2013 ([www.pavelzelezny.cz](http://www.pavelzelezny.cz))\n\n## Requirements ##\n\n[Nette Framework 2.0.12](http://nette.org) or higher. (PHP 5.3 edition)\n\n## Documentation ##\n\nSimple DebugBar to show content of session.\n\n## Instalation ##\n\nPrefered way to intall is by [Composer](http://getcomposer.org)\n\n	{\n		\"require\":{\n			\"zeleznypa/nette-session-debug-bar\": \"dev-master\"\n		}\n	}\n\n## Setup ##\n\nTo load SessionPanel into the DebugBar by insert following code into config.neon\n\n```neon\ncommon:\n	services:\n		sessionPanel:\n			class: \\Zeleznypa\\Nette\\Diagnostics\\SessionPanel\n			arguments:\n				- @application\n				- @session\n\n	nette:\n		debugger:\n			strictMode: true\n			bar:\n				- @sessionPanel\n```\n\nYou can also specify section to hide in debugbar by add setup section in service definition.\n\n```neon\ncommon:\n	services:\n		sessionPanel:\n			class: \\Zeleznypa\\Nette\\Diagnostics\\SessionPanel\n			setup:\n				- hideSection(\'Nette.Http.UserStorage/\')\n				- hideSection(\'Nette.Forms.Form/CSRF\')\n			arguments:\n				- @application\n				- @session\n```',	'{\"github\":{\"composer\":{\"name\":\"composer.json\",\"path\":\"composer.json\",\"sha\":\"e22e5ca07aed7c318f94b54332f895158e543899\",\"size\":610,\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/api.github.com\\/repos\\/zeleznypa\\/nette-session-debug-bar\\/contents\\/composer.json?ref=master\",\"html_url\":\"https:\\/\\/github.com\\/zeleznypa\\/nette-session-debug-bar\\/blob\\/master\\/composer.json\",\"git_url\":\"https:\\/\\/api.github.com\\/repos\\/zeleznypa\\/nette-session-debug-bar\\/git\\/blobs\\/e22e5ca07aed7c318f94b54332f895158e543899\",\"download_url\":\"https:\\/\\/raw.githubusercontent.com\\/zeleznypa\\/nette-session-debug-bar\\/master\\/composer.j