(237,	237,	'vojtech-dobes',	'nette-goto-panel',	'Provides interface to go to any destination within Nette Framework application.',	'MARKDOWN',	NULL,	4,	18,	4,	6,	1,	NULL,	'nette,debugging,panel',	'## For Nette Framework\n\nProvides interface to go to any destination within app.\n\n## Installation\n\n1. Get the source code:\n	* Move `GotoPanel.php` to your libs directory.\n	* Add `\"Clevisaci/GotoPanel\": \"*\"` to your `composer.json`.\n2. Register `GotoPanel` as component (e.g. in `BasePresenter`).\n3. Force initialization in `startup()`.\n\n```php\nprotected function startup()\n{\n	parent::startup();\n	$this[\'gotoPanel\'];\n}\n\nprotected function createComponentGotoPanel()\n{\n	return new GotoPanel;\n}\n```\n\n![Panel used to show link](http://i46.tinypic.com/66gj5z.png)\n',	'{\"github\":{\"composer\":{\"name\":\"composer.json\",\"path\":\"composer.json\",\"sha\":\"7a9b8fc05019dcc7949aa0bf0fe7cb2714427e9a\",\"size\":552,\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/api.github.com\\/repos\\/vojtech-dobes\\/nette-goto-panel\\/contents\\/composer.json?ref=master\",\"html_url\":\"https:\\/\\/github.com\\/vojtech-dobes\\/nette-goto-panel\\/blob\\/master\\/composer.json\",\"git_url\":\"https:\\/\\/api.github.com\\/repos\\/vojtech-dobes\\/nette-goto-panel\\/git\\/blobs\\/7a9b8fc05019dcc7949aa0bf0fe7cb2714427e9a\",\"download_url\":\"https:\\/\\/raw.githubusercontent.com\\/vojtech-dobes\\/nette-goto-panel\\/master\\/composer.json\",\"type\":\"file\",\"content\":\"ewogICAgIm5hbWUiOiAidm9qdGVjaC1kb2Jlcy9uZXR0ZS1nb3RvLXBhbmVs\\nIiwKICAgICJkZXNjcmlwdGlvbiI6ICJQcm92aWRlcyBpbnRlcmZhY2UgdG8g\\nZ28gdG8gYW55IGRlc3RpbmF0aW9uIHdpdGhpbiBOZXR0ZSBGcmFtZXdvcmsg\\nYXBwbGljYXRpb24uIiwKICAgICJrZXl3b3JkcyI6IFsibmV0dGUiLCAiZGVi\\ndWdnaW5nIiwgInBhbmVsIl0sCiAgICAiaG9tZXBhZ2UiOiAiaHR0cDovL2dp\\ndGh1Yi5jb20vdm9qdGVjaC1kb2Jlcy9uZXR0ZS1nb3RvLXBhbmVsIiwKICAg\\nICJsaWNlbnNlIjogIk5ldyBCU0QiLAogICAgImF1dGhvcnMiOiBbCiAgICAg\\nICAgewogICAgICAgICAgICAibmFtZSI6ICJWb2p0xJtjaCBEb2JlxaEiLAog\\nICAgICAgICAgICAiZW1haWwiOiAibWVAdm9qd