(257,	259,	'minetro',	'deployer-sandbox',	'FTP deployment (dg) sandbox for your projects',	'MARKDOWN',	NULL,	1,	1320,	1,	0,	0,	NULL,	NULL,	'# Deployer Sandbox\n\n[![Total downloads](https://img.shields.io/packagist/dt/minetro/deployer-sandbox.svg?style=flat-square)](https://packagist.org/packages/minetro/deployer-sandbox)\n[![Latest stable](https://img.shields.io/packagist/v/minetro/deployer-sandbox.svg?style=flat-square)](https://packagist.org/packages/minetro/deployer-sandbox)\n\nBased on [ftp-deployment](https://github.com/dg/ftp-deployment).\n\n## Install\n```sh\n$ composer create-project minetro/deployer-sandbox:~2.1.0 --prefer-dist --no-dev --no-install -v\n```\n\n## Description\n\n### `deployer.phar` (~38kB)\n\nCompiled ftp-deployment into single file without Google-Closure-Compiler and YuiCompressor.\n\n### `deployer.full.phar` (~7.3MB)\n\nCompiled ftp-deployment into single file **with** Google-Closure-Compiler and YuiCompressor.\n\n## Pre-deploy\n\n1. Place to `project/deploy` folder\n2. Set `username`, `password` and `host` in `config.php`\n3. Update `ignore` files/folders in `config.php`\n\n## Deploy\n\n### Test mode\n\n```sh\nphp deploy/deployer.phar deploy/config.php -t \n```\n\n### Deploy mode\n\n```sh\nphp deploy/deployer.phar deploy/config.php \n```\n',	'{\"github\":{\"readme\":{\"name\":\"README.md\",\"path\":\"README.md\",\"sha\":\"a72f7fbef5e3ab32046dfb0c9c2f69d873de2003\",\"size\":1107,\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/api.github.com\\/repos\\/minetro\\/deployer-sandbox\\/contents\\/README.md?ref=master\",\"html_url\":\"https:\\/\\/github.com\\/minetro\\/deployer-sandbox\\/blob\\/master\\/README.md\",\"git_url\":\"https:\\/\\/api.github.com\\/repos\\/minetro\\/deployer-sandbox\\/git\\/blobs\\/a72f7fbef5e3ab32046dfb0c9c2f69d873de2003\",\"download_url\":\"https:\\/\\/raw.githubusercontent.com\\/minetro\\/deployer-sandbox\\/master\\/README.md\",\"type\":\"file\",\"content\":\"IyBEZXBsb3llciBTYW5kYm94CgpbIVtUb3RhbCBkb3dubG9hZHNdKGh0dHBz\\nOi8vaW1nLnNoaWVsZHMuaW