(275,	283,	'HotelQuickly',	'ErrorMonitoring',	'Project for monitoring all errors and exceptions files across Nette projects',	'MARKDOWN',	NULL,	0,	NULL,	0,	0,	0,	NULL,	NULL,	'ErrorMonitoring\r\n===============\r\n\r\nProject for monitoring exception files across projects generated by [Tracy](https://github.com/nette/tracy)\r\n\r\n## Requirements\r\n* PHP >= 5.3\r\n* MySQL >= 5.6\r\n\r\n## Installation\r\n\r\n1. Clone this repository to your local storage\r\n2. Create folders ```log, temp, www_root/webtemp, temp/sessions``` in project root. If working on mac/linux run ```chmod 777 app/changelog && mkdir -m 777 log temp temp/cache www_root/webtemp temp/sessions```\r\n3. Run ```composer install```\r\n4. Create database, and run queries in app/changelog/init.sql\r\n5. Configure database, AWS access keys, hipchat API key and others if neccessary in app/config/config.local.neon (use config.local.template.neon as template)\r\n6. Visit ```localhost/error-monitoring/changelog``` (or appropriate name, depends how do you use your localhost) for additional database table installation\r\n\r\n## Storage for exceptions\r\nCurrently only implementation is AWS S3 storage. Feel free to implement another storage and send pull request.\r\n\r\n## Usage\r\nExceptions are uploaded to AWS S3 storage from other projects using [ErrorCollector](https://github.com/hotelquickly/errorCollector).\r\n\r\nWhen you add ErrorCollector to new project, you need to first hit Scan for Projects button to find new project.\r\nButton Load exceptions will download all not-yet-downloaded exceptions from all projects.\r\n\r\nConfigure cron if you want to automatically download exceptions.\r\n\r\n```\r\n/cron/import/import-files\r\n```\r\n\r\n## AWS S3 Config\r\n\r\nPlace this in config.local.neon\r\n\r\n```\r\nparameters:\r\n        aws:\r\n		    s3:\r\n			    accessKeyId:\r\n			    secretAccessKey:\r\n			    bucket:\r\n			    region:\r\n```\r\n## AWS S3 directory structure\r\nException files from your projects must be stored in this directory structure.\r\n```\r\n<project-name>/exception/<file-name>.html\r\n```\r\nAll files in exception folder will be parsed and moved to archive folder.\r\n```\r\n<project-name>/archive/exception/<file-name>.html\r\n```\r\n\r\n\r\n',	'{\"github\":{\"readme\":{\"name\":\"README.md\",\"path\":\"README.md\",\"sha\":\"c8a63c4c2395af893f12d0447b11286583b6b5ab\",\"size\":1971,\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/api.github.com\\/repos\\/HotelQuickly\\/ErrorMonitoring\\/contents\\/README.md?ref=master\",\"html_url\":\"https:\\/\\/github.com\\/HotelQuickly\\/ErrorMonitoring\\/blob\\/master\\/README.md\",\"git_url\":\"https:\\/\\/api.github.com\\/repos\\/HotelQuickly\\/ErrorMonitoring\\/git\\/blobs\\/c8a63c4c2395af893f12d0447b11286583b6b5ab\",\"download_url\":\"https:\\/\\/raw.githubusercontent.com\\/HotelQuickly\\/ErrorMonitoring\\/master\\/README.md\",\"type\":\"file\",\"content\":\"RXJyb3JNb25pdG9yaW5nDQo9PT09PT09PT09PT09PT0NCg0KUHJvamVjdCBm\\nb3IgbW9uaXRvcmluZyBleGNlcHRpb24gZmlsZXMgYWNyb3NzIHByb2plY3Rz\\nIGdlbmVyYXRlZCBieSBbVHJhY3ldKGh0dHBzOi8vZ2l0aHViLmNvbS9uZXR0\\nZS90cmFjeSkNCg0KIyMgUmVxdWlyZW1lbnRzDQoqIFBIUCA+PSA1LjMNCiog\\nTXlTUUwgPj0gNS42DQoNCiMjIEluc3RhbGxhdGlvbg0KDQoxLiBDbG9uZSB0\\naGlzIHJlcG9zaXRvcnkgdG8geW91ciBsb2NhbCBzdG9yYWdlDQoyLiBDcmVh\\ndGUgZm9sZGVycyBgYGBsb2csIHRlbXAsIHd3d19yb290L3dlYnRlbXAsIHRl\\nbXAvc2Vzc2lvbnNgYGAgaW4gcHJvamVjdCByb290LiBJZiB3b3JraW5nIG9u\\nIG1hYy9saW51eCBydW4gYGBgY2htb2QgNzc3IGFwcC9jaGFuZ2Vsb2cgJiYg\\nbWtkaXIgLW0gNzc3IGxvZyB0ZW1wIHRlbXAvY2FjaGUgd3d3X3Jvb3Qvd2Vi\\ndGVtcCB0ZW1wL3Nlc3Npb25zYGBgDQozLiBSdW4gYGBgY29tcG9zZXIgaW5z\\ndGFsbGBgYA0KNC4gQ3JlYXRlIGRhdGFiYXNlLCBhbmQgcnVuIHF1ZXJpZXMg\\naW4gYXBwL2NoYW5nZWxvZy9pbml0LnNxbA0KNS4gQ29uZmlndXJlIGRhdGFi\\nYXNlLCBBV1MgYWNjZXNzIGtleXMsIGhpcGNoYXQgQVBJIGtleSBhbmQgb3Ro\\nZXJzIGlmIG5lY2Nlc3NhcnkgaW4gYXBwL2NvbmZpZy9jb25maWcubG9jYWwu\\nbmVvbiAodXNlIGNvbmZpZy5sb2NhbC50ZW1wbGF0ZS5uZW9uIGFzIHRlbXBs\\nYXRlKQ0KNi4gVmlzaXQgYGBgbG9jYWxob3N0L2Vycm9yLW1vbml0b3Jpbmcv\\nY2hhbmdlbG9nYGBgIChvciBhcH