(281,	291,	'viktorbezdek',	'jade-latte',	'Extension allowing usage of Latte templates syntax from Nette framework in Jade templates.',	'MARKDOWN',	NULL,	1,	NULL,	1,	1,	0,	NULL,	NULL,	'# jade-latte\n\n> Extension allowing usage of Latte templates syntax from Nette framework in Jade templates.\n\n[![Code Climate](https://codeclimate.com/github/viktorbezdek/jade-latte/badges/gpa.svg)](https://codeclimate.com/github/viktorbezdek/jade-latte) [![Dependency Status](https://gemnasium.com/viktorbezdek/jade-latte.svg)](https://gemnasium.com/viktorbezdek/jade-latte) [![Build Status](https://travis-ci.org/viktorbezdek/jade-latte.svg?branch=master)](https://travis-ci.org/viktorbezdek/jade-latte) [![Coverage Status](https://coveralls.io/repos/viktorbezdek/jade-latte/badge.svg?branch=master&service=github)](https://coveralls.io/github/viktorbezdek/jade-latte?branch=master)\n\n## What it does\n\n+ Extends Jade functionality to play nice with [Latte](https://latte.nette.org) templates from [Nette](https://nette.org) \n+ Latte expressions in attributes are not escaped\n+ Inline latte expressions in to-be-escaped content not escaped\n+ Fixed Jade bug in mixins, when using namespaced attributes `+mixin(n:href=\"{$whatever->whenever}\")`\n+ Adds filter for PHP supporting blocks, expressions, inline expressions with tweaked solution from [jade4php](https://github.com/BookArt/jade4php)\n\n## What it doesn\'t do\n\n+ Latte block can\'t nest with latte at the moment\n\n## Usage\n\ninstall: `npm install jade-latte`\ntest: `mocha test`\n\n### In templates\n\n+ See file `test/mixin-test.jade`\n\n### With Jade API\n\n```js\nvar assert = require(\'assert\'),\n	jade = require(\'jade\');\n\nrequire(\'../index\')(jade);\n\nvar html = jade.renderFile(__dirname + \'/my_file.jade\');\n\n// rendered html\nconsole.log(html);\n```\n\n### With Gulp\n\n```js\ngulp.src(\"*.jade\")\n	.pipe(plugins.jade({\n		jade: require(\'jade-latte\')(require(\'jade\')),\n	}))\n	.pipe(gulp.dest(\'./build/\'));\n```\n\n## L