(282,	292,	'natocTo',	'Elixir-met-Nette',	'Little helper how to use Laravel Elixir with Nette Framework.',	'MARKDOWN',	NULL,	0,	NULL,	0,	0,	0,	NULL,	NULL,	'## Elixir met Nette\r\n\r\nThis may help you use awesome [Laravel Elixir](https://github.com/laravel/elixir) with [Nette framework](https://github.com/nette/nette) project.\r\n\r\n## Instalation\r\n\r\nDownload, copy to project root directory and run..\r\n\r\n```shell\r\n$ npm install\r\n```\r\n\r\nYou have to install [Node](http://nodejs.org/download/) on your machine before you run \"npm install\".\r\n\r\nAlso Is useful add resources and new created node_modules directory to .gitignore file.\r\n\r\n## How to use\r\n\r\nJust run your task by..\r\n\r\n```shell\r\n$ gulp\r\n```\r\n\r\nIf you also want minify your css / js file..\r\n\r\n```shell\r\n$ gulp --production\r\n```\r\n\r\nOr make gulp watch your assets and do magic automatically\r\n\r\n```shell\r\n$ gulp watch\r\n```\r\n\r\n\r\nFor more information look at brilliant [Elixir documentations](http://laravel.com/docs/5.1/elixir).\r\n\r\n## Enjoy \r\n\r\n',	'{\"github\":{\"readme\":{\"name\":\"readme.md\",\"path\":\"readme.md\",\"sha\":\"33691d515c66a19e7cb45591814ec88f9d3fc74a\",\"size\":837,\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/api.github.com\\/repos\\/natocTo\\/Elixir-met-Nette\\/contents\\/readme.md?ref=master\",\"html_url\":\"https:\\/\\/github.com\\/natocTo\\/Elixir-met-Nette\\/blob\\/master\\/readme.md\",\"git_url\":\"https:\\/\\/api.github.com\\/repos\\/natocTo\\/Elixir-met-Nette\\/git\\/blobs\\/33691d515c66a19e7cb45591814ec88f9d3fc74a\",\"download_url\":\"https:\\/\\/raw.githubusercontent.com\\/natocTo\\/Elixir-met-Nette\\/master\\/readme.md\",\"type\":\"file\",\"content\":\"IyMgRWxpeGlyIG1ldCBOZXR0ZQ0KDQpUaGlzIG1heSBoZWxwIHlvdSB1c2Ug\\nYXdlc29tZSBbTGFyYXZlbCBFbGl4aXJdKGh0dHBzOi8vZ2l0aHViLmNvbS9s\\nYXJhdmVsL2VsaXhpcikgd2l0aCBbTmV0dGUgZnJhbWV3b3JrXShodHRwczov\\nL2dpdGh1Yi5jb20vbmV0dGUvbmV0dGUpIHByb2plY3QuDQoNCiMjIEluc3Rh\\nbGF0aW9uDQoNCkRvd25sb2FkLCBjb3B5IHRvIHByb2plY