(285,	295,	'newPOPE',	'nette-angularjs-sandbox',	'Sandbox project using Nette Framework and AngularJS.',	'MARKDOWN',	NULL,	13,	NULL,	13,	0,	2,	NULL,	NULL,	'# Sandbox with [Nette Framework](http://nette.org) & [AngularJS](http://angularjs.org/)\n\n**TODO** add some basic informations\n\n## Install\nProject has some system dependencies:  \n- [Twitter Bower](http://twitter.github.com/bower/)  \n- [Composer](http://getcomposer.org/)  \n- [Testacular](http://vojtajina.github.com/testacular/)\n\n### Run install script\n\nRun ```./scripts/install.sh```\n\n- install Nette Framework via Composer  \n- install [Angular, jQuery, Bootstrap.css]\n- create empty ```config.local.neon```\n\n### Development server\n\nCommand ```./scripts/web-server.sh``` starts the local development server on ```localhost:3000```\nand App run on ```localhost:3000/src/www/```\n\n### Run e2e tests\n\nRun```./scripts/e2e-tests.sh```\n\n**Note:** _Before e2e tests starded local development server must run._\n\n',	'{\"github\":{\"readme\":{\"name\":\"README.md\",\"path\":\"README.md\",\"sha\":\"c45acf451f19c36a0a172410ce2206fdd06798bd\",\"size\":802,\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/api.github.com\\/repos\\/newPOPE\\/nette-angularjs-sandbox\\/contents\\/README.md?ref=master\",\"html_url\":\"https:\\/\\/github.com\\/newPOPE\\/nette-angularjs-sandbox\\/blob\\/master\\/README.md\",\"git_url\":\"https:\\/\\/api.github.com\\/repos\\/newPOPE\\/nette-angularjs-sandbox\\/git\\/blobs\\/c45acf451f19c36a0a172410ce2206fdd06798bd\",\"download_url\":\"https:\\/\\/raw.githubusercontent.com\\/newPOPE\\/nette-angularjs-sandbox\\/master\\/README.md\",\"type\":\"file\",\"content\":\"IyBTYW5kYm94IHdpdGggW05ldHRlIEZyYW1ld29ya10oaHR0cDovL25ldHRl\\nLm9yZykgJiBbQW5ndWxhckpTXShodHRwOi8vYW5ndWxhcmpzLm9yZy8pCgoq\\nKlRPRE8qKiBhZGQgc29tZSBiYXNpYyBpbmZvcm1hdGlvbnMKCiMjIEluc3Rh\\nbGwKUHJvamVjdCBoYXMgc29tZSBzeXN0ZW0gZGVwZW5kZW5jaWVzOiAgCi0g\\nW1R3aXR0ZXIgQm93ZXJdKGh0dHA6Ly90d2l0dGVyLmdpdGh1Yi5jb20vYm93\\nZXIvKSAgCi0gW0NvbXBvc2VyXShodHRwOi8vZ2V0Y29t