(286,	296,	'chemix',	'grunt-nette-basepath',	'Grunt plugin to update paths for concat, uglify and cssmin where is nette variable $basePath',	'MARKDOWN',	NULL,	9,	NULL,	9,	0,	1,	NULL,	NULL,	'# grunt-nette-basepath\n\n> Grunt plugin to updates paths for concat, uglify and cssmin where is nette variable $basePath\n\n\n## Getting Started\nThis plugin requires Grunt `~0.4.4` and use-min `^2.4.0`\n\nIf you haven\'t used [Grunt](http://gruntjs.com/) before, be sure to check out the [Getting Started](http://gruntjs.com/getting-started) guide, as it explains how to create a [Gruntfile](http://gruntjs.com/sample-gruntfile) as well as install and use Grunt plugins. Once you\'re familiar with that process, you may install this plugin with this command:\n\n```shell\nnpm install grunt-nette-basepath --save-dev\n```\n\nOne the plugin has been installed, it may be enabled inside your Gruntfile with this line of JavaScript:\n\n```js\ngrunt.loadNpmTasks(\'grunt-nette-basepath\');\n```\n\n## The \"netteBasePath\" task\n\n### Overview\nIn your project\'s Gruntfile, add a section named `netteBasePath` to the data object passed into `grunt.initConfig()`.\n\nfull example on [github.com/chemix/Nette-Grunt](https://github.com/chemix/Nette-Grunt)\n\n```js\ngrunt.initConfig({\n  ...\n  netteBasePath: {\n    task: {\n      basePath: \'www\',\n      options: {\n        removeFromPath: [\'app/templates/\']\n      }\n    }\n  },\n  ...\n})\n```\n\n```coffee\n  ...\n  netteBasePath:\n    task:\n      basePath: \'www\'\n      options:\n        removeFromPath: [\'app/template/\']\n  ...\n```\n\n\nMultiple replacements\n\n```coffee\n  ...\n  netteBasePath:\n    taskCore:\n      basePath: \'www\'\n      options:\n        removeFromPath: [\'app/template/\']\n    taskLibs:\n      basePath: \'www/components\'\n      options:\n        searchPattern: \'{$incPath}\'\n  ...\n```\n\n\n## Release History\n- 0.3.0: Support for another replace path search string, multiple replaces\n- 0.2.0: Update for grunt-usemin 2.1.0\n- 0.1.0: Initial release',	'{\"github\":{\"readme\":{\"name\":\"README.md\",\"path\":\"README.md\",\"sha\":\"98e6512e0205e5c25e0b8cdaf31832367d928481\",\"size\":1748,\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/api.github.com\\/repos\\/chemix\\/grunt-nette-basepath\\/contents\\/README.md?ref=master\",\"html_url\":\"https:\\/\\/github.com\\/chemix\\/grunt-nette-basepath\\/blob\\/master\\/README.md\",\"git_url\":\"https:\\/\\/api.github.com\\/repos\\/chemix\\/grunt-nette-basepath\\/git\\/blobs\\/98e6512e0205e5c25e0b8cdaf31832367d928481\",\"download_url\":\"https:\\/\\/raw.githubusercontent.com\\/chemix\\/grunt-nette-basepath\\/master\\/README.md\",\"type\":\"file\",\"content\":\"IyBncnVudC1uZXR0ZS1iYXNlcGF0aAoKPiBHcnVudCBwbHVnaW4gdG8gdXBk\\nYXRlcyBwYXRocyBmb3IgY29uY2F0LCB1Z2xpZnkgYW5kIGNzc21pbiB3aGVy\\nZSBpcyBuZXR0ZSB2YXJpYWJsZSAkYmFzZVBhdGgKCgojIyBHZXR0aW5nIFN0\\nYXJ0ZWQKVGhpcyBwbHVnaW4gcmVxdWlyZXMgR3J1bnQgYH4wLjQuNGAgYW5k\\nIHVzZS1taW4gYF4yLjQuMGAKCklmIHlvdSBoYXZlbid0IHVzZWQgW0dydW50\\nXShodHRwOi8vZ3J1bnRqcy5jb20vKSBiZWZvcmUsIGJlIHN1cmUgdG8gY2hl\\nY2sgb3V0IHRoZSBbR2V0dGluZyBTdGFydGVkXShodHRwOi8vZ3J1bnRqcy5j\\nb20vZ2V0dGluZy1zdGFydGVkKSBndWlkZSwgYXMgaXQgZXhwbGFpbnMgaG93\\nIHRvIGNyZWF0ZSBhIFtHcnVudGZpbGVdKGh0dHA6Ly9ncnVudGpzLmNvbS9z\\nYW1wbGUtZ3J1bnRmaWxlKSBhcyB3ZWxsIGFzIGluc3RhbGwgYW5kIHVzZSBH\\ncnVudCBwbHVnaW5zLiBPbmNlIHlvdSdyZSBmYW1pbGlhciB3aXRoIHRoYXQg\\ncHJvY2VzcywgeW91IG1heSBpbnN0YWxsIHRoaXMgcGx1Z2luIHdpdGggdGhp\\ncyBjb21tYW5kOgoKYGBgc2hlbGwKbnBtIGluc3RhbGwgZ3J1bnQtbmV0dGUt\\nYmFzZXBhdGggLS1zYXZlLWRldgpgYGAKCk9uZSB0aGUgcGx1Z2luIGhhcyBi\\nZWVuIGluc3RhbGxlZCwgaXQgbWF5IGJlIGVuYWJsZWQgaW5zaWRlIHlvdXIg\\nR3J1bnRmaWxlIHdpdGggdGhpcyBsaW5lIG9mIEphdmFTY3JpcHQ6CgpgYGBq\\ncwpncnVudC5sb2FkTnBtVGFza3MoJ2dydW50LW5ldHRlLWJhc2VwYXRoJyk7\\nCmBgYAoKIyMgVGhlICJuZXR0ZUJhc2VQYXRoIiB0YXNrCgojIyMgT3ZlcnZp\\nZXcKSW4geW91ciBwcm9qZWN0J3MgR3J1bnRmaWxlLCBhZGQgYSBzZWN0aW9u\\nIG5hbWVkIGBuZXR0ZUJhc2VQYXRoYCB0byB0aGUgZGF0YSBvYmplY3QgcGFz\\nc2VkIGludG8gYGdydW50LmluaXRDb25maWcoKWAuCgpmdWxsIGV4YW1wbGUg\\nb24g