(290,	302,	'nette',	'netbeans-plugin',	'Nette Framework support in NetBeans IDE',	'RAW',	NULL,	67,	NULL,	67,	18,	8,	NULL,	NULL,	'\n\nSupport for Nette is now included with NetBeans. For reporting use NetBeans issue tracker.\n========\n\nThis repository is old and not maintained.\n\nCustom build\n============\n\n0. Because of plugin certification you must make your own build without the certificate. To allow that remove lines \'keystore=nbproject/private/keystore\' and \'nbm_alias=myself\' from the \'nbproject/project.properties\' file.\n\n1. download NetBeans IDE with JavaSE and PHP module\n2. clone git repository - git clone https://github.com/nette/netbeans-plugin.git\n3. run NetBeans IDE and open cloned repository as a project\n4. right click on the project name in the \'Project window\'\n5. left click on \'Create NBM\'\n6. when building is complete a \'*.nbm\' file is generated in the \'./build\' directory\n7. done :-) \n',	'{\"github\":{\"readme\":{\"name\":\"README.txt\",\"path\":\"README.txt\",\"sha\":\"fa433b64c2ee134263a9e132ce13075fd7e6c9a4\",\"size\":777,\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/api.github.com\\/repos\\/nette\\/netbeans-plugin\\/contents\\/README.txt?ref=master\",\"html_url\":\"https:\\/\\/github.com\\/nette\\/netbeans-plugin\\/blob\\/master\\/README.txt\",\"git_url\":\"https:\\/\\/api.github.com\\/repos\\/nette\\/netbeans-plugin\\/git\\/blobs\\/fa433b64c2ee134263a9e132ce13075fd7e6c9a4\",\"download_url\":\"https:\\/\\/raw.githubusercontent.com\\/nette\\/netbeans-plugin\\/master\\/README.txt\",\"type\":\"file\",\"content\":\"CgpTdXBwb3J0IGZvciBOZXR0ZSBpcyBub3cgaW5jbHVkZWQgd2l0aCBOZXRC\\nZWFucy4gRm9yIHJlcG9ydGluZyB1c2UgTmV0QmVhbnMgaXNzdWUgdHJhY2tl\\nci4KPT09PT09PT0KClRoaXMgcmVwb3NpdG9yeSBpcyBvbGQgYW5kIG5vdCBt\\nYWludGFpbmVkLgoKQ3VzdG9tIGJ1aWxkCj09PT09PT09PT09PQoKMC4gQmVj\\nYXVzZSBvZiBwbHVnaW4gY2VydGlmaWNhdGlvbiB5b3UgbXVzdCBtYWtlIHlv\\ndXIgb3duIGJ1aWxkIHdpdGhvdXQgdGhlIGNlcnRpZmljYXRlLiBUbyBhbGxv\\ndyB0aGF0IHJlbW92ZSBsaW5lcyAna2V5c3RvcmU9bmJwcm9qZWN0L3ByaXZh\\nd